reviewText: Yes the sound is terrible, could not even watch it, not worth 1.00. I was very disappointed. Tried to write the company who produced it no good.

I thought this was a how to video as well, I reserved it at the library and was excited to get it thinking I would be doing qi gong.  I popped it in the VCR and it was just mostly discussion which isn't so bad, because I learned more about qi gong, but my overall thing is I wanted to actually practice qi gong.
